# CCW
# Approach: always staying infront of the side and looking directly at the side
o Cube

# Front
v  1.0 -1.0  1.0
v  1.0  1.0  1.0
v -1.0  1.0  1.0
v -1.0 -1.0  1.0

# Back
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v -1.0  1.0 -1.0
v  1.0  1.0 -1.0
v  1.0 -1.0 -1.0

# UV Corners
vt 1.0  0.0
vt 1.0  1.0
vt 0.0  1.0
vt 0.0  0.0

vn  0.0  0.0  1.0
vn  0.0  0.0 -1.0
vn  0.0  1.0  0.0
vn  0.0 -1.0  0.0
vn  1.0  0.0  0.0
vn -1.0  0.0  0.0

s off

#        6--------7
#       /|       /|
#      3--------2 |
#      | |      | |
#      | 5------|-8
#      |/       |/
#      4--------1

# +Z
f 1/1/1 2/2/1 3/3/1
f 3/3/1 4/4/1 1/1/1

# -Z
f 5/1/2 6/2/2 7/3/2
f 7/3/2 8/4/2 5/1/2

# +Y
f 2/1/3 7/2/3 6/3/3
f 6/3/3 3/4/3 2/1/3

# -Y
f 4/1/4 5/2/4 8/3/4
f 8/3/4 1/4/4 4/1/4

# +X
f 8/1/5 7/2/5 2/3/5
f 2/3/5 1/4/5 8/1/5

# -X
f 4/1/6 3/2/6 6/3/6
f 6/3/6 5/4/6 4/1/6

